{"tid":2122785,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"15歲男學生鎚擊飛虎隊成員被控襲警 葉啟亮裁決罪名成立 還押候判至8月7日判刑","createTime":"2020-07-24T07:51:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T13:52:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"437c071322419dc9a0b34639a03e243e10c23e23","tid":2122785,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:51:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/7346\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F7346&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6Ax%2F1T5MpBrdTD4T%2Fai5QWg%3D&h=cc07e1d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/7346</a><br />\n<br />\n#屯門裁判法院第七庭 <br />\n#葉啟亮裁判官<br />\n#裁決<br />\n<br />\n*(16)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：襲警<br />\n<br />\n案情：10月7日在新界屯門青山公路新墟段與屯門鄉事會路交界，使用木錘襲擊警員X。<br />\n<br />\n【速報】罪名成立<br />\n<br />\n索取感化報告、更生中心報告、勞教中心報告，期間還押候判<br />\n押後至8月7日1030屯門裁判法院第七庭判刑<br />\n<br />\n&quot;辯方結案陳詞指，X供稱案發時被告右手持鎚急跑及施襲，但被告右手因傷不能用力，況且X隸屬警隊最精銳的特警隊，不可能被當時年僅15歲、身形瘦弱的被告襲擊。辯方又指多名警員證人的證供前後矛盾及「好多甩漏」，法庭不可依賴。案件7月24日裁決。&quot;"},{"pid":"1e9d7005307ccdb58568013b39bd6e682348746b","tid":2122785,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08554689b89f4c763084b988d6eb90c3c25c75a7","tid":2122785,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:54:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /